data.description: Stunning 4-Bedroom, 2.5-Bathroom Home with Office, Open Kitchen, and More!Welcome to your dream home! This exquisite 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence offers an abundance of space, style, and comfort. With a spacious open kitchen, a large breakfast area, relaxing keeping room, formal dining room, and an office, this home is perfect for modern living and entertaining. Plus, well-appointed coffee/beverage bar adds a touch of luxury to your lifestyle. Upstairs you will find a true owners' retreat in the oversized primary bedroom with sitting area, a spacious primary bathroom with double vanities, separate shower, garden tub and water closet, with a walk-in closet with an abundance of space. You will also find upstairs the other three bedrooms, one of which has its own vanity area that leads into the Jack and Jill bathroom. There is no need to carry laundry downstairs with a laundry room with custom built-in cabinets located on the second floor. The outdoors can be enjoyed in the large backyard or screened in patio.
